OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying very
OL,6,Fwarm and humid overnight. Elevated
OL,7,Fthunderstorms spreading northwards,
OL,8,Fturning very gusty with thunder,
OL,9,Flightning and hail likely. Low cloud
OL,10,Fmoving into Cornwall through the early
OL,11,Fhours of the morning.
OL,12,
OL,13,CFriday:FAlthough temperatures falling,
OL,14,Fstaying very warm with humidity levels
OL,15,Fremaining high. Cloud across Cornwall
OL,16,Flifts through the morning, leaving
OL,17,Fplenty of strong sunshine for all.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
