OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FStaying
OL,6,Fhot into the weekend, but temperatures
OL,7,Fslowly coming down; feeling fresher by
OL,8,FSunday. Dry for many but turning
OL,9,Fcloudier into the new week.
